metadata.description:
The iPass of Metaverse launched by Nobody Labs in July 2022 hopes to start a new Metaverse journey with more families. 
Nobody Labs is an avid metaverse explorer, which counts many years of investment in research and development. With its unique computing power and technology, Nobody Labs provides energy-efficient computing infrastructure (XXXXX) and solution for the Metaverse digital world (XXXXXverse) .
